{"tid":1337111,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「人宣」翻牆大陸人怎樣看香港警察","createTime":"2019-07-21T07:55:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T09:51:38.000Z","uid":274452,"like":201,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e6fce036ff4f206366014874e4af7598f95f536d","tid":1337111,"uid":274452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xR31r5x472w&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxR31r5x472w%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=4cEDjPrkdumF5Vl7%2FlTeckPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=b19e3060\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xR31r5x472w&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n片尾個男人同佢一講共產黨就要求我DEL片<br />\n但我緊係冇DEL，有下集<br />\n可以聽下佢點睇大陸政府<br />\n佢知咩事，不過大陸人好叻扮傻<br />\n同埋有問左位大陸遊客點睇社會信用評級<br />\n<br />\n出完去番黎POST<br />\n不過唔知個CHANNEL會唔會比老共搞，大家幫幫手<br />\n我會努力做人宣，大家有咩想比大陸人知，我就比佢地知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ffd1503ffe5dd14f26ad1f270c4e867ab6fe33","tid":1337111,"uid":38109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T07:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aebdea39e00eff7d079f78a2602da669d326369b","tid":1337111,"uid":274452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:00:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57bed42a2e3098fbcb89dadba116dcb883022d5a","tid":1337111,"uid":274452,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54838d53b2e5f0761659637eac1d0b09fc0a0800","tid":1337111,"uid":45358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T08:13:31.000Z","msg":"Lm 發完夢睇"},{"pid":"83c6c369dc338803ace6ae6028ca7f9526ac1723","tid":1337111,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply